author: Today I Found Out
description:
Dark Rides or 'Ghost Trains' have been an integral part of Disney Parks since 1955. Known as 'Highways and Horizons', The Futurama showcased how traffic issues might be solved in the future aka, the wonderful world of 1960.

Author: Gilles Messier
Host: Simon Whistler
Editor: Daven Hiskey
Producer: Samuel Avila
title: Futurama- The Most Incredible Dark Ride You’ve Never Heard Of
